CAT3DAnnotationFilterHdr.Title: Annotation Sets Filter
CAT3DAnnotationFilterHdr.ShortHelp: Lets you filter the annotation sets, annotations displayed in the 3D area, and the technological attributes.
CAT3DAnnotationFilterHdr.LongHelp: Expand the required section and specify the required filtering options.
CAT3DAnnotationOpenFavoriteCtxHdr.Title: Open in Favorite Context
CAT3DAnnotationOpenFavoriteCtxHdr.ShortH: Lets you open the favorite context attached to the required 3DShape.
